{"type": "article", "id": 27141, "title": "提高生活品质，给你几个小物做参考丨这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2016-05-21T08:21:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5504, "name": "礼物"}, {"id": 11551, "name": "父亲节"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 297, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702165616DGJzngA6ldB8RwkO.jpg", "contents": "\r\n\r\n<p class=\"\">本周的推荐其实没有什么特别的主题，或者说，是我们长期以来一直使用的主题：让生活通过设计更美好一点。总得来说，便利度和质感是两个很重要的因素。请看看我们这周挑选的东西。</p>\r\n<p>          </p>\r\n<h2>Globe by Jean-Marie Massaud</h2>\r\n<p>意大利的老牌箱包品牌 Fabbrica Pelletterie Milano （FPM）的设计师系列有很多经典产品，比如联合 nendo 推出可将盖子卷开的旅行箱，非常巧妙。法国设计师 Jean-Marie Massaud 的<a href=\"http://shop.fpm.it/collezione/globe/8/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Globe </a>系列更具典雅和时尚，箱子表面使用了十字交叉的纹路，依然保留了流畅感和亮度， logo 就在其中一个交叉口上，很特别。箱子的内部很简单，也因此拥有更大的容积。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165602TxKXUpLGoPvhQOnm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165602Eo4mWtLOhlInD7eS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165603cyuodIE2st7pWeHw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>WINGBACK SOFA by Tom Dixon</h2>\r\n<p>英国设计师 Tom Dixon 的<a href=\"http://www.tomdixon.net/row/furniture/chairs/wingback-sofa-blue-copper-legs-1.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"> WINGBACK SOFA </a>是他最具代表性的作品之一，从 17 世纪俱乐部风格的沙发入手，将座位降低靠背加长，使沙发看起来非常宽大，从侧面看又多了一份古典优雅。材料上使用丹麦品牌 Kvadrat 的面料，保证了舒适的感受。如果家里空间足够，是一个很不错的选择。<br></p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165603OayRKhjnYlip472b.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72521739\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165603x8Khkm0NflvA4dan.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72521739\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165604qbUioc5XsDWpzVEC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72521739\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021656046xMRkboGpjUuOdeh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72521739\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021656053NDTcwb4eyIkqlaj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72521739\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>银制茶具 by Marc Newson</h2>\r\n<p>茶具是最保险的送礼佳品，这套茶具是由现苹果设计师 Marc Newson 和银器工匠共同完成。纯银的质感让它拥有简洁的现代美，茶具底部的藤编可以隔热，但同样也是一种对传统手工的回应，它带给人了一种仪式感。茶具一共有 5 件，不过这套茶具是限量的，只能提供参考。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165605nJuEkIt6R2YfBD3r.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67359413\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021656066Ql1zj0kGWuhaKrb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63202934\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165606saodIYn1cyfbiTmM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165607JCyEk0MqPgtDLIvH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72371638\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165607zb1VYlrm8yhiudNt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165608hvZljmLCT9DFe10N.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72738386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>          </p>\r\n<h2>ChopTainer by ThinkHat</h2>\r\n<p>这个名为 ChopTainer 的容器是下厨的好帮手。和普通的菜篮子不同，ChopTainer 很符合“砧板伴侣”这样的定位：贴着砧板侧放后，你可以很轻松地收集切好的食材。针对需要滤干的食材，也设计了绿色的滤器版。为了防滑，两种容器都使用了橡胶材质的底座。除此之外，它们可以像碗一样叠在一起，完全不会占用厨房的空间。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/choptainer-cutting-board-extension-bins#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，最低的套装价为 20 美元。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165608cVWoaN03qSr2QEHb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59677419\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165609DLtprTiC4EYBh3Hc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59677419\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165609UuY80XpLftyQbv9D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59677419\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021656103OyDa74TuBC9Ej28.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021656108DKicA0fNBZQW3Gt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165610et9DcG4nwlJVvECS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>EPIQUAL by EPIQUAL</h2>\r\n<p>          </p>\r\n<p>要提升生活品质，一把既实用又美观的牙刷是一个不错的选择。EPIQUAL 的设计团队希望通过这个产品改变人们对于牙刷的偏见：即便是不使用的时候，它们也可以和装修漂亮的浴室环境融为一体。从外观上看，EPIQUAL 就像一件纤细的艺术品，底座本身也可以当作牙刷架使用。EPIQUAL 还提供了价格低廉的刷头补充方案供你选择，订购之后每三个月你就会收到一套新的刷头。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/epiqual/epiqual-the-most-beautiful-design-toothbrush-ever\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 20 美元。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165611Hdy1uW6K4gXo0t2G.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59411765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165611uJF8XPZrExAypdmg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165612n2aIgkdmAytVJUTR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67058824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165612Q7ENfJZDYpPoW4Vt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165613gbRY4ySBtzqHN9P1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021656132j485d7keBKiDUX3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.48823529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>桃花芯木艺术扇 by 乐途</h2>\r\n<p>          </p>\r\n<p class=\"\">适度怀旧也是一种生活乐趣。乐途推出的这一系列风扇均采用桃花芯木由工匠手工打造，复古的造型或许让你和市面上其他平庸或者高科技造型的风扇隔离开来，有一种进入老电影的感觉。这是它的<a href=\"http://z.jd.com/project/details/53907.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，最低价为 179 元（包含邮费），风扇的底座还可以根据需要刻上文字。</p>\r\n<p>          </p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165614ji3Z8HfTEzupWkUc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8789916\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165614yHZwJ1E4s5tRleSc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87837838\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165614bPmDCv6Tnef1BQJG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88087248\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021656158JB0ZHVAb6p7mENy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.34639175\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165616LRwBt05xrqNejYi9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73218997\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\r\n\r\n"}